Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左脸的十字伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.45,0:01:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你就是\N大名鼎鼎的绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.32,0:02:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是来抢赤空最后的名刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.79,0:02:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要的是别的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要赤空的刀就要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.43,0:02:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你要先把那孩子放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.16,0:02:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十话\N可怕的无情刺客\N十本刀和张的死斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不必为了一个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.27,0:02:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大打出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的逆刃刀已断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已没有武器可决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.85,0:02:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打败你是轻而易举的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不必打就已分出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就替志志雄杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易拿到一把上乘好剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.83,0:02:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我试试它的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就从你开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试试杀小孩的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就来场正大光明的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.18,0:03:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的剑已断  你又挟有人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子叫什么正大光明决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你有多厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能打赢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以打赢斋藤的牙突剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.21,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不再考虑清楚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的刀已断  绝对打不赢我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.99,0:03:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会后悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这把就是赤空打的杀人奇剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.49,0:03:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人体若被此剑所伤\N若不即时治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.07,0:03:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤口将会腐烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.31,0:04:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你还是执迷不悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.42,0:04:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下  我马上救你下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说放下就放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我张某当成什么人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊织 再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是存心跟我过不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就让你看看我的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么招式尽管使出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别尽是些不中用的花样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是要开始来真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道绯村怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.27,0:05:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜也没用  我们到了就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村的剑已经断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.14,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷你真小气\N也不借他一把剑用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 他们开始打起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.35,0:05:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村这家伙真是沉不住气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不用刀决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村就不会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心那男人身上的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.93,0:05:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是家父赤空改良的\N后期型杀人奇剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我张十刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.68,0:05:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要开始出招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙带了刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的爱刀 杀人奇剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薄刃乃太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差一点  就打到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.50,0:06:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你好运  这次我不会放过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人奇剑  薄刃乃太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.84,0:06:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一把极薄极锋利的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.51,0:06:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以快速自由变幻招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.21,0:06:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人捏把冷汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被那把薄刃乃太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砍到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候多出了看好戏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的人就快滚到一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打不赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的剑 放弃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.64,0:06:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的大蛇剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.81,0:06:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管不了了  救伊织要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他现在正专心决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.24,0:06:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意力没有在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用这个时候救伊织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想害死绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.39,0:07:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明知他现在处于下风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小心了我要上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没打完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙紧迫盯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有叫他决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他自己要决斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.81,0:07:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你救子心切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.12,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村现在是为了谁而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你忘了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知死活的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个小鬼的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值得你这么做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说他是小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.64,0:08:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但对我来说\N他是无可取代的新生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快把伊织放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.52,0:08:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么革命家的自大论调
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的时代已经结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是志志雄的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的薄刀乃太刀的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你安心受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.70,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你真是执迷不悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造时代的不是刀剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.31,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是拥有刀剑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别再废话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快纳命来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这看好戏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存心来找死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.57,0:08:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青空  快把伊织带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.61,0:09:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下伊织  我来救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知死活的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.08,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先父以制造刀剑\N来创造新时代的用意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要被他溜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造新时代的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够守护和平的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就托付给此人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.17,0:09:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将父亲的最后一把刀\N交给这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和伊织一定要守护\N这个和平的新时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是交差攻法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村没刀怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果输的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.86,0:10:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙还是不死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你还能撑到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次我不会再放过你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.34,0:10:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  胜算不大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有刀就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是家父的最后一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你使用它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是赤空的名刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好利用这个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好见识一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.87,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这把刀还是那把刀厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.11,0:10:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了  绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了刀你就赢定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.75,0:11:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村不能拔刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村已立下誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.69,0:11:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不再使用\N逆刃刀以外的剑杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.07,0:11:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都什么时候  还管这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.14,0:11:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在如果他不杀人就会被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.61,0:11:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果绯村用了这把刀杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.04,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就要重新恢复杀手的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是杀手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.02,0:11:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后他就无法再成为普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.89,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个杀手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在发什么呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你忘记怎么杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.01,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就表演给你看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就拿这个你所谓的新生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,示范给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼发威了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别上他的圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.77,0:12:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看老子怎么加倍还给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从后面解决你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么招势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从哪学来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.22,0:12:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流 龙卷闪旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解决了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村  你看这把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到赤空打的最后一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.56,0:15:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一向只打杀人剑的父亲\N会在最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炼了一把逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.07,0:15:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这支白木柄\N居然能耐得住绯村的力道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斩我千银发  炼刀几星霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽为子孙恨  但为后代福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:16:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤空花费毕生之精力\N打造了这些剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.83,0:16:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己虽得承受被儿子憎恨的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.46,0:16:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却能给后代子孙造福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.17,0:16:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可能是赤空去世前\N刻下的诗句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.31,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是父亲有所觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.28,0:16:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本家父为自己的铸刀功力深以为傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本以为只要有刀剑\N就可创造和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到事实与现实刚好相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.82,0:16:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此父亲心中充满了\N深深的悔恨与希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次打造了这把御神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.69,0:16:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次打造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲打御神刀时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事先就打造了二把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.84,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么这把就是第二把逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.94,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这把是比逆刃刀\N更厉害的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你收下吧  绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.48,0:17:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成先父的遗志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在好不容易\N才刚打胜鸟羽伏见之仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.33,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎能就此罢手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你洗手不干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以后想做什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后 我不再杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要保护好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.11,0:17:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身边的人就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.44,0:17:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果世事像你所想的就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界上就不会有那么多坏人杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.68,0:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么多好人被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.12,0:17:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你真的已作此决定了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.16,0:17:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你不再需要刀剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.96,0:17:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姑且你就带这把刀在身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.17,0:17:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许它能帮你实现自己的志愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有一天刀断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还需要一把好刀时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.88,0:18:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就来京都找我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切如你所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打了一把新的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔再见  叔叔再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来京都都三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.49,0:18:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都没见到剑心的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别自作主张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人到街上乱找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你找到剑心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我有的是时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上街逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好会遇到剑心也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是四乃森苍紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在这干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.70,0:19:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看那家伙贼头贼脑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道又想找剑心什么麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.34,0:19:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张十刀已被警察带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是比古清十郎的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.02,0:19:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这地方可能不太好找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.99,0:19:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫的事我帮不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.44,0:20:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记你的  绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.01,0:20:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也别忘记我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村  马上要吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你上哪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.16,0:20:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又要上哪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.46,0:20:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再给你们添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.30,0:20:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就此道别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.87,0:20:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不必这么快就走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你是不是杀手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.51,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有使命要去完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道你是绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.59,0:20:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在东京的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.52,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有人跟我说过同样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到到了京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.60,0:21:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又听到你这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村不只是个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心地善良的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.71,0:21:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也是个有理想有正义感的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.15,0:21:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他这次去能够平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.66,0:21:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会放你一人\N去承担那么大的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.13,0:21:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让我和你一起\N分担这些重任吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.49,0:22:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个走路不长眼睛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.49,0:22:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.73,0:22:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你先撞到我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.19,0:22:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样对姑娘说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为我们在赶时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.23,0:22:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我跟丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.33,0:22:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.57,0:22:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.54,0:22:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识绯村剑心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.71,0:22:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我  他人在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.85,0:22:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.19,0:22:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是绯村说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.99,0:22:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在东京认识的女孩子
